### ══════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════════

### ── Full recall report — all 29 golden set entries
### Expected response shape:
### {
###   "overallRecall": 0.87,          ← must be >= 0.85 to pass
###   "overallPrecision": 0.82,
###   "totalPassed": 25,
###   "totalEntries": 29,
###   "meetsTarget": true,
###   "byCategory": {
###     "PERFORMANCE":    { "recall": 0.95, "precision": 0.90, "passed": 4, "total": 4 },
###     "MAINTENANCE":    { "recall": 0.75, "precision": 0.80, "passed": 2, "total": 3 },
###     "OWNERSHIP_COST": { "recall": 0.90, "precision": 0.85, "passed": 3, "total": 3 },
