GET http://localhost:8080/api/eval/vehicles/recall/report

###

### ── Category drill-down queries (run after report to debug failing categories)
### If MAINTENANCE recall is low → run these individually to see which chunks fail

### Maintenance category queries
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "what does the 30000 mile service cost on the BMW M3",
  "topK": 3,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

###

POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "spark plug replacement interval BMW",
  "topK": 3,
  "mode": "HYBRID"
}

###

### If CROSS_CHUNK recall is low → run these

POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "fast sports car that wont break the bank",
  "topK": 5
}

###

POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask
Content-Type: application/json

