### Edge case validation

### EDGE-004: nonsense query — must return empty or very low score results
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "xyzabc vehicle",
  "topK": 3
}

###

### EDGE-005: short token "M3" — tests BM25 fallback to vector
POST http://localhost:8080/vehicles/bmw-m3-2025-competition/ask
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "question": "M3",
  "topK": 3,
  "mode": "BM25"
}
